# Daily Email Summary AI Agent

An AI-powered automation workflow that collects emails, processes content intelligently, generates concise summaries, and delivers them directly to Telegram.

## Overview

This workflow automatically:

1. Runs on a scheduled trigger
2. Retrieves incoming Gmail messages
3. Processes email data using custom code
4. Uses AI to analyze and summarize content
5. Sends clean summaries directly to Telegram

## Workflow Architecture

Schedule Trigger
↓
Gmail Message Retrieval
↓
Data Processing Layer
↓
AI Agent Analysis
↓
Telegram Notification

